1.15.2.0.1.5.1_beta:
Changed Update Checker to show changelog in-game
Fixed Variants of Acacia Wood, Birch Wood, Dark Oak Wood, Jungle Wood, Oak Wood and Spruce Wood not burning in fire
Fixed Stone Brick Slab crafting recipe
Fixed many recipe inconsistencies
Support for 1.15 (1.15.2-31.1.0)
1.15.2.0.1.5_beta:
Beta Update
Initial beta release
Added Slab, Stairs and Wall Variants for End Stone
Added Slab, Stairs and Fence Variants for Acacia Wood, Birch Wood, Dark Oak Wood, Jungle Wood, Oak Wood and Spruce Wood
Added Stairs and Wall Variants for Cut Red Sandstone, Cut Sandstone and Smooth Stone
Added Wall Variant for Dark Prismarine, Polished Andesite, Polished Diorite, Polished Granite, Prismarine Bricks, Purpur Block, Quartz Block, Smooth Quartz, Smooth Red Sandstone, Smooth Sandstone and Stone
Added Fence Variant for Red Nether Bricks
Added Slab, Stairs and Wall Variants for Cracked Stone Bricks Variants (suggested by SeanMaxMyla)
Added two hidden Variants
Added Reward System
Added Update Checker
Added 'Render16x'
Changed some Minecraft recipes to avoid conflicts
Support for 1.15 (1.15.2-31.1.0)
